  "prompt": "What will be the PSU cut off for the all categories?",
  "response": "The PSU (Public Sector Undertaking) cut-off marks vary based on the specific PSU, the examination conducted (such as GATE, UGC NET, etc.), the category of candidates (General, OBC, SC, ST, EWS, etc.), and the year. Each PSU sets its own cut-off criteria based on factors like the number of vacancies, the difficulty level of the exam, and the overall performance of candidates.\n\nFor the most accurate and updated information regarding PSU cut-offs for a specific exam or year, it is best to check the official websites of the PSUs or the examination bodies. Additionally, online forums and educational websites often provide insights and updates on cut-offs after the results are announced.",
